      <para styleclass="Heading1">Error XS0151</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">A value of an integral type expected</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">A variable was used in a situation where an integral data type was required. For more information, see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Types">Types</link>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Example</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">This error can occur when there is no conversion or if the available implicit conversions result in an ambiguous situation. The following sample generates XS0151.</para>
